<br/>
<div class="phototagleft">
</div>
</div>
<p style="margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in"><strong>Lopamudra Basu</strong> is professor of English at the University of Wisconsin&ndash;Stout. She is author of <em>Ayad Akhtar, the American Nation and Its Others after 9/11: Homeland Insecurity</em> (2018). She has reviewed books for <em>World Literature Today, India Currents</em>, and <em>Ariel: A Review of International English Literature</em>.</p>
<div class="clear"></div>
